<div class="yousay ">
  Hi, Iâ€™m calling to ask about getting the COVID vaccine for a person over 65.
  Could I please speak to the pharmacist on duty?
</div>

<div class="instructions">Once you reach the right person, ask</div>
<div class="yousay ">
  Are you currently offering COVID-19 vaccines to members of the public?
</div>
<form id="callScriptForm">
  <div id="noOptions" class="btn-group" role="group">
    <input
      class="btn-check"
      type="radio"
      id="noNever"
      name="yesNoSelect"
      value="No: will never be a vaccination site"
    />
    <label class="btn btn-outline-danger" for="noNever"> Never </label>

    <input
      class="btn-check"
      type="radio"
      id="noPrivate"
      name="yesNoSelect"
      value="No: not open to the public"
    />
    <label class="btn btn-outline-danger" for="noPrivate">
      Private facility
    </label>
    <input
      class="btn-check"
      type="radio"
      name="yesNoSelect"
      id="noStaffOnly"
      value="No: only vaccinating staff"
    />
    <label class="btn btn-outline-danger" for="noStaffOnly"> Only staff </label>

    <input
      class="btn-check"
      type="radio"
      name="yesNoSelect"
      id="noHCWOnly"
      value="No: only vaccinating health care workers"
    />
    <label class="btn btn-outline-danger" for="noHCWOnly">
      Only health care workers
    </label>
  </div>

  <div id="yesOptions" class="btn-group" role="group">
    <input
      type="radio"
      name="yesNoSelect"
      value="Yes"
      id="yesJustYes"
      class="btn-check"
    />
    <label class="btn btn-outline-success" for="yesJustYes"> Yes we are </label>
    <input
      type="radio"
      id="yesSoon"
      value="Yes: coming soon"
      class="btn-check"
      name="yesNoSelect"
    />
    <label class="btn btn-outline-success" for="yesSoon">
      We will be soon
    </label>
  </div>

  <div id="vaccinatingPublicScript">
    <div class="yousay ">
      How old do seniors need to be to get vaccinated?
    </div>
    <div class="btn-group" role="group">
      <input
        class="btn-check"
        type="radio"
        name="ageSelect"
        value="Yes: vaccinating 65+"
        id="over65"
      />
      <label class="btn btn-outline-warning" for="over65"> 65 </label>
      <input
        class="btn-check"
        type="radio"
        name="ageSelect"
        value="Yes: vaccinating 75+"
        id="over75"
      />
      <label class="btn btn-outline-warning" for="over75"> 75 </label>
      <input
        class="btn-check"
        type="radio"
        name="ageSelect"
        value="Yes: vaccinating 80+"
        id="over80"
      />
      <label class="btn btn-outline-warning" for="over80"> 80 </label>
      <input
        class="btn-check"
        type="radio"
        name="ageSelect"
        value="Yes: vaccinating 85+"
        id="over85"
      />
      <label class="btn btn-outline-warning" for="over85"> 85 </label>
      <input
        class="btn-check"
        type="radio"
        name="ageSelect"
        value="no_seniors"
        id="noSeniors"
      />
      <label class="btn btn-outline-warning" for="noSeniors">
        Not vaccinating seniors
      </label>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="yousay ">Thanks! Do they need an appointment</div>

  <div class="btn-group" role="group">
    <input
      class="btn-check"
      type="radio"
      name="appointment"
      value="Yes: walk-ins accepted"
      id="apptWalkin"
      data-bs-toggle="collapse"
      href="#appointmentInfo"
    />
    <label class="btn btn-outline-secondary" for="apptWalkin">
      Walkins are welcome</label
    >
    <input
      class="btn-check"
      type="radio"
      name="appointment"
      value="Yes: appointment required"
      id="apptReqd"
    />
    <label class="btn btn-outline-secondary" for="apptReqd">
      Appointment Required</label
    >
  </div>
  <div id="appointmentInfo">
    <input
      type="checkbox"
      class="btn btn-check"
      name="appointmentsFull"
      id="apptFull"
    />
    <label class="btn btn-outline-secondary" for="apptFull"
      >The schedule is full</label
    >
    <div class="yousay ">How should they make the appointment</div>
    <div class="btn-group" role="group">
      <input
        class="btn-check"
        type="radio"
        name="appointmentMethod"
        id="methodCounty"
        value="county"
      /><label for="methodCounty" class="btn btn-outline-secondary"
        >County website</label >
      <input
        class="btn-check"
        type="radio"
        name="appointmentMethod"
        id="methodMyTurn"
        value="myturn"
      /><label for="methodMyTurn" class="btn btn-outline-secondary" >myturn.ca.gov</label>
      <input
        class="btn-check"
        type="radio"
        name="appointmentMethod"
        id="methodPhone"
        value="phone"
      /><label for="methodPhone" class="btn btn-outline-secondary">phone</label>
      <input
        class="btn-check"
        type="radio"
        name="appointmentMethod"
        id="methodWeb"
        value="web"
      /><label for="methodWeb" class="btn btn-outline-secondary">web</label>
      <input
        class="btn-check"
        type="radio"
        name="appointmentMethod"
        id="methodOther"
        value="other"
      /><label for="methodOther" class="btn btn-outline-secondary"
        >Another way</label
      >
    </div>
    <input type="text" id="appointmentPhone" class="form-control" placeholder="Appointment phone number" value="{{locationPhone}}"/>
    <input type="text" id="appointmentOtherInstructions" class="form-control" placeholder="Scheduling instructions" />
    <input type="text" id="appointmentWebsite" class="form-control" placeholder="Appointment website" />
  </div>
  <div class="restrictions">
    <div class="yousay ">
      Are you folks vaccinating all Californians or are there limits on who you
      can vaccinate?
    </div>
    <div class="">
      <input class="btn-check" type="checkbox" id="veteransOnly" /><label
        class="btn btn-outline-primary"
        for="veteransOnly"
        >Veterans only</label
      >
      <input class="btn-check" type="checkbox" id="patientsOnly" /><label
        class="btn btn-outline-primary"
        for="patientsOnly"
        >Current patients only</label
      >
      <input class="btn-check" type="checkbox" id="countyOnly" /><label
        class="btn btn-outline-primary"
        for="countyOnly"
        >County residents only</label
      >
    </div>
    <div class="instructions small secondary">
      If they say anything that's not on the list, mention it in the public
      notes.
    </div>

    <div class="yousay ">
      Can you confirm that your address is {{ locationAddress }}
    </div>
    <div class="instructions">
      If that's wrong,
      <a
        target="_blank"
        class="text-muted small"
        href="https://airtable.com/shrY44NvEjHBscrOH?prefill_Location={{locationId}}&prefill_Type=Incorrect+contact+information"
        >Report an error</a
      >
    </div>
  </div>

  <div>
    <div id="callScriptPublicNotes">Public notes</div>
    <div
      class="input form-control form-control-sm"
      role="textbox"
      contenteditable
    >{{ locationPublicNotes }}</div>
  </div>

  <div>
    <div id="callScriptPrivateNotes">Private notes</div>
    <div
      class="input border border-warning form-control form-control-sm"
      role="textbox"
      contenteditable
    >{{ locationPrivateNotes }}</div>
  </div>
  <div class="d-grid gap-2 col-6 mx-auto row">
    <input
      type="button"
      class="btn btn-primary"
      id="scoobyRecordCall"
      value="Send report"
    />
  </div>
</form>
